            "url": "https://www.nicematin.com",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a regional newspaper for two ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "departments ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "in France publishing about 600 articles a day, from 180 journalists. Solutions journalism is a small team of three journalists and a video-journalist.  They produce very long reads, which are the keystone of their subscriber ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "#MonJournal",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://www.nicematin.com/sujet/monjournal",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " offer‚Ä¶",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It's the 5 Ws with one addition: what are we doing now. They're looking for well-defined issues they can have an impact on. They announce the chosen topic via a Facebook Live. Once the readers choose the next topic, they'll produce between 10 and 15 articles, some in collaboration with the readers. After the investigation, they'll have a debate and a \"making of\" article explaining the difficulties and successes. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/corinne_podger/status/1103322093968674818",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AMalval?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AMalval</a> from the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/solutionsjournalism?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#solutionsjournalism</a> team at Nice Matin in France on how they approach covering solutions journalism stories - key slides 2/2. Interesting that there&#39;s pushback from newsroom even though engagement &amp; revenue both positively impacted. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/newsrw?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#newsrw</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/zcRSx4wnaZ\">pic.twitter.com/zcRSx4wnaZ</a></p>&mdash; ùêÇùê®ùê´ùê¢ùêßùêßùêû ùêèùê®ùêùùê†ùêûùê´üì±üéì (@corinne_podger) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/corinne_podger/status/1103322093968674818?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
        "embedType": "rich"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A good solutions journalism piece looks at one person's solution, including proofs of result, now points of view on the issue - and an examination of the limitations of the issue, to avoid slipping into an advertorial tone. Solutions journalism is not just \"good news\" journalism - it's more than that. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/TweeterStewart/status/1103321327522533381",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Great slide from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AMalval?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AMalval</a> at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/newsrw?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#newsrw</a> presentation on solutions journalism. <a href=\"https://t.co/xnhrczbWGI\">pic.twitter.com/xnhrczbWGI</a></p>&mdash; Peter Stewart - voice &amp; video (@TweeterStewart) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweeterStewart/status/1103321327522533381?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
        "embedType": "rich"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Solutions journalism readers are over twice as likely as average article readers to subscribe. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/joyjenkins/status/1103323420115300352",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The solutions journalism at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Nice_Matin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Nice_Matin</a> has drawn 10,000 subscribers in 3 years - 32 months of gains - through focusing on going a step beyond classic investigative reporting, not producing advertorials or ‚Äúfeel-good news,‚Äù says <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AMalval?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AMalval</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/newsrw?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#newsrw</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/k4MT62zXYC\">pic.twitter.com/k4MT62zXYC</a></p>&mdash; Joy Jenkins (@joyjenkins) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/joyjenkins/status/1103323420115300352?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
        "embedType": "rich"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "However, the idea is hard to sell to the rest of the staff. It's hard work to research solutions. The border with advertorial is a daily struggle  - the \"happy news\" temptation is real. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Jonathan Paterson",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
