        "type": "heading",
        "tag": "h2",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "BBC News",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "heading",
        "tag": "h3",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2019/03/IMG_0353.jpg",
        "cardWidth": "wide"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "How do we deal with important, negative stories in the age of the Like button, when downbeat stories often don't spread? Focus on the solutions. Tell people how hospitals are making sure the right people come to accident and emergency:",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/726484101071300/",
        "html": "<div id=\"fb-root\"></div>\n<script async=\"1\" defer=\"1\" src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/nl_NL/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v3.2\"></script><div class=\"fb-video\" data-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/726484101071300/\"><blockquote cite=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/726484101071300/\" class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/726484101071300/\">The A&amp;E with a nurse on the front door</a><p>How &#039;gatekeeper&#039; nurses are cutting waiting times in one A&amp;E.\n\n(Via BBC Lifestyle &amp; Health News) bbc.in/2FSl08u</p>Geplaatst door <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/\">BBC News</a> op Dinsdag 22 januari 2019</blockquote></div>",
        "embedType": "video"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Show Norway's bottle deposit scheme: ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/10155614321468649/",
        "html": "<div id=\"fb-root\"></div>\n<script async=\"1\" defer=\"1\" src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/nl_NL/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v3.2\"></script><div class=\"fb-video\" data-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/10155614321468649/\"><blockquote cite=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/10155614321468649/\" class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/videos/10155614321468649/\">Norway&#039;s plastic waste solution...</a><p>Has Norway found a way to deal with their plastic waste problem?\n\n(BBC Science News)</p>Geplaatst door <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnews/\">BBC News</a> op Woensdag 7 februari 2018</blockquote></div>",
        "embedType": "video"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "They don't deny or ignore the problem - it's the starting point for the story. But they provide a new take - a solution. Sometimes the solution is the way into explaining the problem - like the community taxi service that highlights the bus cuts coming from austerity. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"400\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/av/embed/p06tw7nq/46445069\"></iframe>"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "How do we develop a commissioning model that delivers solutions journalism like that? ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Sean Dagan Wood",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
