          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " to make it a community-owned businesses. Print circulation has doubled, web visits are up by over 60% - and they're profitable for the first time since the relaunch. ",
            "type": "text",
